data.description: Welcome to Rio Bravo Country Club! Introducing a captivating opportunity that boast over 2,600 SF on a large corner lot just a few steps away from the club house: Home features-A splendid one-story 4 bedroom split wing, plus an ensuite office with a separate entrance to the bathroom that has double sinks in all three bathrooms. Luxury private jacuzzi tub in primary bathroom. Formal living, formal dining, huge family room with fireplace. Kitchen has beautiful granite counter tops with backsplash. Large walk-in pantry and breakfast area. Inside laundry room with sink and a spacious 3 car garage. This home is most definitely a show stopper and it wont last long!! Did I mention the electricity is paid for, for the next 20+ years so that means no bill!!Sunrun owns the solar panels they replace and repair all the solar equipment at no charge to the home owner for the next 22 years!! So contact your favorite realtor today.
